@startuml coro_awaitable
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Мост callback → co_await (connect_async)

participant "coroutine" as Coro
participant "connect_awaitable" as Await
participant "tcp_socket" as Sock
participant "event_loop" as Loop

Coro -> Await : co_await connect_async(sock, loop, ep, token)
Await -> Await : await_ready() == false
Await -> Await : bind_cancel(token → cancel_io)
Await -> Sock : async_connect(..., resume, on_error)
note over Sock, Loop
  По завершении connect
  вызывается h.resume()
end note
Sock --> Await : resume coroutine
Await -> Coro : await_resume()\nили rethrow exception

@enduml
